    <h2 class="w3-wide">Registration</h2>
    <p>The deadline for regular registration is the <span class="w3-tag w3-red w3-large">1<sup>st</sup> of August, 2025</span>. The meeting will be limited to a maximum of 25 participants, with everybody being given a chance to present their science case (~15+5 min).</p>
